{"tid":1249703,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我希望大家有定心理準備 聽日民意會向返對家小小","createTime":"2019-06-21T19:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:57:51.000Z","uid":44925,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4679a9f9401b8b68395adf6785f21345b58946e8","tid":1249703,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:35:24.000Z","msg":"因為有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB</span></span>助攻<br />\n<br />\n但記住<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔緊要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好因為聽日小小民意反彈而蝕氣 相反我地要更加再接再厲 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫人出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解?? 就好似股票咁 係高位實會有回落<br />\n但今次我地既支持位係相當穩陣 只要隻股票大家仲覺得係掂 回落左都會升返<br />\n<br />\n最忌係咩??? 睇錯走勢而唔出黎<br />\n<br />\n記住   <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">出黎</span></span><br />\n我地自己掌握返民意"},{"pid":"fa143d645b4ceec7b85d825d1d8bf6006eb428f0","tid":1249703,"uid":44925,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:41:27.000Z","msg":"下一步<br />\n<br />\n行動唔可以停<br />\n同時輿論戰唔可以停<br />\n大家一定要受得住民意回落果一下低潮期<br />\n唔好灰 一灰而唔出 佢地就會步步進逼 然後大規模清算<br />\n<br />\n行動可以試唔同野 不過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以停</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長遠:<br />\n要諗點樣對付CCTVB"},{"pid":"597dea2fff0af0cc8c72512c7e909569a21aad94","tid":1249703,"uid":44925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:56:45.000Z","msg":"大家有定心理準備聽日CCTVB會扭曲哂所有事實<br />\n<br />\nSave哂所有長輩圖準備!"},{"pid":"41ec8c4bfa4889b01301b510cd826678f0ec0b76","tid":1249703,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26ac2a8350177c65b68513009d0d3ab9da6968a7","tid":1249703,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"推一推 大家一定要硬食幾野輿論攻擊<br />\n而唔係因為輿論而咩都唔夠膽做"},{"pid":"10b508561b4dbb72ced80aa4f80fc64a5bf5